    - rid: 107151358184390656
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 45
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390657
          output: 'The prophet speaks with undeniable conviction, enough to stir
            the hearts of all present. Even if his divine visions do not truly descend
            from the Beholder, it is undeniable that his words inspire the faithful!

            [Gained
            30 Zeal]'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390658
          output: 'What a disaster! The prophet proved to be little more than a raving
            lunatic. The moment he was granted the floor, he began to babble of apocalyptic
            dooms and other absurdities. The people took no liking to his sermons;
            it will take much effort to restore their trust.

            [Lost
            30 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 5
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390659
          - rid: 107151358184390660
          output: 'A miracle! As the prophet addressed the masses, the heavens parted
            and a shaft of light descended from the very center of the sun. His words
            echoed throughout the Ocularium, and the sound of trumpets could be heard
            from the firmament. This man is truly a chosen vessel of the Beholder!
            Long live our sect!

            [Gained 50 Zeal & Boon]'
